quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  106,1,"Makapantag ko kiyasinanad o manga Quraish,-"
  106,2,"So kiyasinanad iran ko katho­togalin ko kapanununggao niyan a go so kakhakayao niyan,-"
  106,3,"Na Showasowata iran so Kad­nan a ungkai a Baitollah,"
  106,4,"So migai kiran sa Pangunung­kun po-on ko kaor, go miyakasarig kiran pho-on ko kaluk."
  107,1,"Ino kiyatokawan Ka so gi-i niyan pakambokhagun so balas (ko Akhirat)?"
  107,2,"Na giyoto man so Puphanaromag ko Wata a ilo,"
  107,3,"Go di niyan iphamintal so kapakakana ko Miskin."
  107,4,"Na sangat a siksa a ruk o manga Barasambayang,"
  107,5,"A so siran na so Sambayang iran na pakalilipatan niran,"
  107,6,"So siran na maki-ilailain siran,"
  107,7,"Go u-urunun niran so kakha­ piya-an!"
  108,1,"Mata-an! A Sukami na inibu­gai Ami Ruka (Ya Muhammad) so madakul (a Mapiya)"
  108,2,"Na Shambayang Ka makapan­tag ko Kadnan Ka, go Khorbang­ ka."
  108,3,"Mata-an! A so Pukhararangit Ruka na sukaniyan i da a tondasi­yan."